icateType","line":250,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.isPredicateType","doc":"Return `true` if `type` is a predicate.\nExamples: `Nat → Prop`, `Prop`, `Int → Bool → Prop`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.isPredicateType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">isPredicateType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.lean#L231-L248","name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.instantiateForall","line":231,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.instantiateForall","doc":"Given a LCNF `type` of the form `forall (a_1 : A_1) ... (a_n : A_n), B[a_1, ..., a_n]` and `p_1 : A_1, ... p_n : A_n`,\nreturn `B[p_1, ..., p_n]`.\n\nRemark: similar to `Meta.instantiateForall`, buf for LCNF types.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.instantiateForall\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">instantiateForall</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ps</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.lean#L219-L229","name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.isTypeFormerType","line":219,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.isTypeFormerType","doc":"Return `true` if `type` is a LCNF type former type.\n\nRemark: This is faster than `Lean.Meta.isTypeFormer`, as this\nassumes that the input `type` is an LCNF type.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.isTypeFormerType\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>.<span class=\"name\">LCNF</span>.<span class=\"name\">isTypeFormerType</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.lean#L189-L215","name":"Lean.Compiler.LCNF.joinTypes?","line":189,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.joinTypes?","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Compiler/LCNF/Types.html#Lean.Compiler.LCNF.joinTypes?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Compiler</span>